{"tid":2152931,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"理大學生記者興訟追 788 元維修費　律政司申移交高院審理","createTime":"2020-08-12T09:05:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-12T12:35:00.000Z","uid":56115,"like":370,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":61,"replies":[{"pid":"67e38ceb605b72a61e594366814677c88e367b21","tid":2152931,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T09:05:59.000Z","msg":"香港理工大學學生會校園電台記者稱去年 11月，在旺角用手機拍攝警方驅散人群期間，突然遭警員發射胡椒彈，使其手機損毀，遂入稟小額錢債審裁處，追討共 788 元維修費及訟費。案件今日在小額錢債審裁處再訊，<span class=\"red\">律政司以案件涉及複雜及重大的法律爭議，申請將案件移交高等法院審理</span>，學生記者則反對，認為將幾百元的賠償轉至涉上萬訟費的高院審理並不合理。案件押後至 10 月 21 日再訊，屆時將爭議是否移交高院。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E7%A8%B1%E6%8E%A1%E8%A8%AA%E6%99%82%E9%81%AD%E8%AD%A6%E5%B0%84%E8%83%A1%E6%A4%92%E7%90%83%E8%87%B4%E6%89%8B%E6%A9%9F%E6%90%8D%E6%AF%80-%E7%90%86%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E8%88%88%E8%A8%9F%E8%BF%BD-788-%E5%85%83%E7%B6%AD%E4%BF%AE%E8%B2%BB-%E5%BE%8B%E6%94%BF%E5%8F%B8%E7%94%B3%E7%A7%BB%E4%BA%A4%E9%AB%98%E9%99%A2%E5%AF%A9%E7%90%86/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E6%258E%25A1%25E8%25A8%25AA%25E6%2599%2582%25E9%2581%25AD%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%25B0%2584%25E8%2583%25A1%25E6%25A4%2592%25E7%2590%2583%25E8%2587%25B4%25E6%2589%258B%25E6%25A9%259F%25E6%2590%258D%25E6%25AF%2580-%25E7%2590%2586%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E8%25A8%2598%25E8%2580%2585%25E8%2588%2588%25E8%25A8%259F%25E8%25BF%25BD-788-%25E5%2585%2583%25E7%25B6%25AD%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E8%25B2%25BB-%25E5%25BE%258B%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%258F%25B8%25E7%2594%25B3%25E7%25A7%25BB%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E9%25AB%2598%25E9%2599%25A2%25E5%25AF%25A9%25E7%2590%2586%2F&d=xm989VH5JK0%2BokU91cWWf5nDkpC49KclrNwegNic%2Fqo%3D&h=cd9ba024\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E6%258E%25A1%25E8%25A8%25AA%25E6%2599%2582%25E9%2581%25AD%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%25B0%2584%25E8%2583%25A1%25E6%25A4%2592%25E7%2590%2583